items.title: Awesome Powershell
items.content_text:
### Commandline Productivity

*   [Jump-Location (⭐472)](https://github.com/tkellogg/Jump-Location) - PowerShell `cd` that reads your mind. [Autojump (⭐17k)](https://github.com/wting/autojump) implementation for PowerShell. **`UNMAINTAINED`**
*   [Microsoft.PowerShell.UnixCompleters (⭐113)](https://github.com/PowerShell/Modules/tree/master/Modules/Microsoft.PowerShell.UnixCompleters) - Get parameter completion for native Unix utilities. Requires zsh or bash.
*   [PSDepend (⭐291)](https://github.com/RamblingCookieMonster/PSDepend/) - PowerShell Dependency Handler
*   [PSScriptTools (⭐964)](https://github.com/jdhitsolutions/PSScriptTools) - A set of of PowerShell functions you might use to enhance your own functions and scripts or to facilitate working in the console.

### Data

*   [hjson-powershell (⭐6)](https://github.com/TomasBouda/hjson-powershell) - Simple powershell module for conversion between [HJSON](https://hjson.github.io/) and JSON.
*   [ImportExcel (⭐2.6k)](https://github.com/dfinke/ImportExcel) - Module to import/export Excel spreadsheets, without Excel.
*   [powershell-yaml (⭐471)](https://github.com/cloudbase/powershell-yaml) - PowerShell CmdLets for YAML format manipulation.
*   [PSWriteHTML (⭐937)](https://github.com/EvotecIT/PSWriteHTML) - PSWriteHTML is a PowerShell module allowing you to create HTML easily.
*   [PSWritePDF (⭐215)](https://github.com/EvotecIT/PSWritePDF) - Module to create, edit, split, merge PDF files on Windows / Linux and MacOS.
*   [PSWriteWord (⭐236)](https://github.com/EvotecIT/PSWriteWord) - Module to create Microsoft Word documents without Microsoft Word installed.

### Frameworks

*   [Kansa (⭐1.6k)](https://github.com/davehull/Kansa) - Incident response framework.

### Interactive Learning

*   [Jupyter-PowerShell (⭐110)](https://github.com/Jaykul/Jupyter-PowerShell) - Jupyter Kernel for PowerShell.

### Logging

*   [PoShLog (⭐217)](https://github.com/PoShLog/PoShLog) - Cross-platform, extensible logging module built upon [Serilog](https://serilog.net).

### Parallel Processing

*   [PSThreadJob (⭐179)](https://github.com/PaulHigin/PSThreadJob) - Module for running concurrent jobs based on threads rather than processes.

### Security

*   [Harness (⭐77)](https://github.com/Rich5/Harness) - Interactive remote PowerShell Payload.
*   [Invoke-Obfuscation (⭐4k)](https://github.com/danielbohannon/Invoke-Obfuscation) - PowerShell Obfuscator.
*   [p0wnedShell (⭐1.5k)](https://github.com/Cn33liz/p0wnedShell) - PowerShell Runspace Post Exploitation Toolkit.
*   [PESecurity (⭐647)](https://github.com/NetSPI/PESecurity) - Module to check if a Windows binary (EXE/DLL) has been compiled with ASLR, DEP, SafeSEH, StrongNaming, and Authenticode.
*   [Powershellery (⭐572)](https://github.com/nullbind/Powershellery) - Powershell scripts used for general hackery.
*   [PowerUpSQL (⭐2.6k)](https://github.com/NetSPI/PowerUpSQL) - Toolkit for Attacking SQL Server.

### Testing

*   [Selenium (⭐475)](https://github.com/adamdriscoll/selenium-powershell) - PowerShell module to run a Selenium WebDriver.
*   [PSScriptAnalyzer (⭐2k)](https://github.com/PowerShell/PSScriptAnalyzer) - PSScriptAnalyzer provides script analysis and checks for potential code defects in the scripts by applying a group of built-in or customized rules on the scripts being analyzed.

### UI

*   [AnyBox (⭐221)](https://github.com/dm3ll3n/AnyBox) - Designed to facilitate script input/output with an easily customizable WPF window.
*   [BurntToast (⭐1.5k)](https://github.com/Windos/BurntToast) - Module for creating and displaying Toast Notifications on Microsoft Windows 10.
*   [Graphical (⭐356)](https://github.com/PrateekKumarSingh/graphical) - Module to plot colorful console 2D Graphs (Scatter, Bar, Line).
*   [GraphicalTools (⭐880)](https://github.com/PowerShell/GraphicalTools) - A module that mixes PowerShell and GUIs! - built on Avalonia and gui.cs.
*   [PS-Menu (⭐259)](https://github.com/chrisseroka/ps-menu) - Simple module to render interactive console menu.
*   [PSWriteColor (⭐184)](https://github.com/EvotecIT/PSWriteColor) - Write-Color is a wrapper around Write-Host allowing you to create nice looking scripts, with colorized output.
*   [Terminal-Icons (⭐2.7k)](https://github.com/devblackops/Terminal-Icons) - Module to show file and folder icons in the terminal.

### Misc

*   [PoshBot (⭐547)](https://github.com/poshbotio/PoshBot) - Powershell-based bot framework.
*   [PoShKeePass (⭐258)](https://github.com/PSKeePass/PoShKeePass) - Module for working with [KeePass](https://keepass.info) databases.

### Architecture and Design

### Frameworks and Stacks

### Planning and Control / Vector Map

*   [global\_racetrajectory\_optimization (⭐525)](https://github.com/TUMFTM/global_racetrajectory_optimization) - This repository contains multiple approaches for generating global racetrajectories.
